      \"At T minus eight minutes, Erik takes his place on the barrow. I then cross over. Emergence is scheduled for level two, visitors' car park block delta three. There will be cameras but no internal guard patrols inside the car park\x{2014}active security is on the perimeter and at the doors.\"
    
  

  
    
      The ferret-faced man nodded. \"Kurt?\"
    
  

  
    
