      \"Not much,\" the Ferret admitted. \"Jurgen?\"
    
  

  
    
      Jurgen shrugged. \"We shoot any witnesses, of course.\" He tapped one trouser pocket, which was cut away to reveal the butt of a silenced pistol peeping out of a leg holster. The uniforms weren't very authentic\x{2014}but then, they only had to mislead witnesses for a few seconds. \"If we can't cross back because of a surveyor's error, we turn the barrow upside down and Kurt stands on it. I ride him. Yes?\"
    
  

  
    
